{
  "texts": [
    "IntraCompBench is designed to stress this regime and to separately probe the two symptoms we target: (1) count failures and (2) semantic mixing.Task 1 -multi-instance accuracy (%) This task isolates count failures.",
    "We sample a single class A from a super-category in Tab.",
    "8 and specify an integer n ∈ {2, 3, 4, 5}.",
    "Now the prompt is formatted as \"A photo of [n] [class A]s\" (e.g., \"A photo of five cats\").",
    "Success requires producing exactly N = n instances of A."
  ]
}